1645	  (\cref{def:gr_glued_scheme}) is separated; equivalently, the diagonal
1646	  \(\Delta : \mathrm{Gr}(r,d) \to \mathrm{Gr}(r,d) \times_{\mathbb{Z}}
1647	  \mathrm{Gr}(r,d)\) is a closed immersion.
